properties.title: The Anthrax
properties.description: Wires In The Walls posted a photo: 25 Perry Avenue...this used to be the infamous punk club "The Anthrax" in its second incarnation. Who did I see here? 76% Uncertain, Zombie Squad, Token Entry, Fugazi, Youth Of Today, ALL, Mr. T Experience, Bad Religion, Swiz, Shelter, Burn, Absolution, Wrecking Crew, Gorilla Biscuits, Dag Nasty...and in no small way, everything on this Flickr stream can be traced back to walking through that door the first time.
